WHITE ASH

Fraxinus americana L.

Plant Symbol = FRAM2 
Contributed By: USDA NRCS National Plant Data 
Center &amp. the Biota of North America Program 
R. Mohlenbrock 
USDA, NRCS, Wetland Science Institute 
