FERNALD’S IRIS 
Iris fernaldii R.C. Foster 
Plant Symbol = IRFE 
 
Contributed by: USDA NRCS National Plant Data 
Center 
Alfred Brousseau 
© Brother Eric Vogel, St. Mary s College 
