                          Plant Guide  
 
  
CHOKECHERRY 
Prunus virginiana L. 
Plant Symbol = PRVI 
 
Contributed by: USDA NRCS Pullman, Washington 
and Manhattan, Kansas Plant Materials Centers and 
Kansas State University Forestry Division 
