                          Plant Guide  
  
BLUE ELDERBERRY 
 
Sambucus nigra L. ssp. 
caerulea (Raf.) R. Bolli 
Plant Symbol = SANIC5 
 
Contributed by: USDA NRCS National Plant Data 
Center &amp. the Biota of North America Program 
 
